title: Max retries exceeded with url
body: If you see the error `[WARN] unable to fetch current market data; skipping: HTTPSConnectionPool(host=market.example.com, port=443): Max retries exceeded with url: / (Caused by NameResolutionError(Failed to resolve market.example.com ([Errno -2] Name or service not known)))`, it means that the market.example.com service has not yet been provisioned in this region. Please ask devops to provision it.
